msgctxt "62\t255"
msgid ""
"Kamurocho attracts all kinds of people.\\n"
"Weak, strong, you name it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "258\t357"
msgid "It really is a jungle out there."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "400\t562"
msgid ""
"But there's one thing everyone\\n"
"who comes here has in common."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "567\t627"
msgid "Which is what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "673\t737"
msgid "A dream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "802\t945"
msgid ""
"Every single person has some\\n"
"grand vision they're reaching for."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "964\t1024"
msgid "Like what?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1029\t1156"
msgid ""
"Landing the perfect woman,\\n"
"hitting it rich, seizing power..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1159\t1333"
msgid ""
"Everyone's got something, no matter\\n"
"how insignificant that something might seem."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1356\t1475"
msgid "But barely a soul actually achieves it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1492\t1583"
msgid "Even so, people don't just abandon their dreams."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1588\t1668"
msgid "They're what keep us trudging onward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1673\t1726"
msgid "You get me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1727\t1787"
msgid "Yeah."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1802\t1901"
msgid "People wanna see those dreams come to fruition."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1908\t2083"
msgid ""
"So what this town needs...\\n"
"is someone who can show them that's possible."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2093\t2174"
msgid "Someone like Arai-aniki?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2179\t2235"
msgid "Bingo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2237\t2368"
msgid ""
"For better or worse,\\n"
"strength is what wins people over."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2385\t2498"
msgid "And Arai-san's got it in spades."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2510\t2570"
msgid "I've seen that first-hand."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2645\t2737"
msgid "A jungle's nothing without its king."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2738\t2854"
msgid "And this town needs a king now more than ever."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2884\t3045"
msgid ""
"Kamurocho's always looked to\\n"
"the yakuza to find its lions."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3064\t3260"
msgid ""
"But Kazuma Kiryu's out of the picture,\\n"
"and nobody's stepped up to fill the void."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3299\t3417"
msgid ""
"Without a leader,\\n"
"even the toughest prides will scatter."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3422\t3502"
msgid "Find a new king somewhere else."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3530\t3633"
msgid "That's, like... pretty deep."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3630\t3712"
msgid "Forget all this nonsense about jungles, though."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3714\t3852"
msgid ""
"What I'm saying is,\\n"
"I'm putting all my chips on Arai-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3873\t3916"
msgid "Got it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3934\t4052"
msgid "I'm in on that dream, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4079\t4159"
msgid "I'll find Arai-aniki, no matter what!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4168\t4281"
msgid "And I'll use this money to make it happen!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4286\t4395"
msgid "Good. Drop me a line if you learn anything."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4400\t4455"
msgid "Of course!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4458\t4520"
msgid "I'm back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4533\t4590"
msgid "Oh, Kido-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4592\t4650"
msgid "Heya."
msgstr ""